data.description: Welcome to 14011 Parksite Woods, your single story dream home in the heart of San Antonio! Nestled on over 1/3 acre in a highly sought-after area, this 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. As you step inside, the recently updated flooring welcomes you, leading to a spacious living area that exudes warmth and charm. The heart of this home is the kitchen, boasting sleek granite countertops and modern appliances. Imagine preparing meals in this cozy kitchen with the convenience of gas cooking. With 2,538 square feet of well-designed living space, this home  provides ample room for relaxation and entertainment. The 5 bedrooms offer versatility, perfect for all types of living situations from nuclear to multigenerational (heck, this could be a single person's dream space with rooms galore). The primary suite is a true retreat, featuring a private escape from the daily hustle and bustle complete with a full bath ensuite and direct access to the outdoors. Car enthusiasts (and storage fanatics alike) will appreciate the oversized 2-car garage, providing ample space for vehicles and overflow belongings. The expansive backyard is an outdoor oasis, backing up to a greenbelt for added privacy and tranquility. Whether you're hosting gatherings or enjoying peaceful Texas nights, this outdoor space is sure to be a favorite. Beyond the architectural aesthetic appeal, this home is situated in a location that combines convenience with a peaceful ambiance. Embrace the sense of community and take advantage of nearby amenities, parks, and top-rated schools. Don't miss this opportunity, schedule a showing today and experience the seamless blend of modern living and timeless comfort in this San Antonio treasure! Don't forget to search for the hidden climate-controlled wine, storage closet!
